[2
Date: Tue 16 Jan 2001 09:29:46 -0500
From: Ms. Anne Roca <rocaanne@paho.org>
Source: PAHO/WHO, Special Program for Health Analysis

Dengue in Central America: The Epidemics of 2000
------------------------------------------------
A complete overview of the dengue fever epidemics that occurred in Central
America in the year 2000 is available in the December issue of the Pan
American Health Organization's Epidemiological Bulletin (Vol. 21, No.
4). The Bulletin is available online in English and Spanish at
<http://www.paho.org/English/SHA/be_v21n4-cover.htm>, and
<http://www.paho.org/Spanish/sha/be_v21n4-cover.htm>
--
Anne Roca
Special Program for Health Analysis
PAHO/WHO
Washington, DC
<rocaanne@paho.org>
